collections.name: Eggolution
collections.description:
Presenting a collection by an unknown author.
In a world overflowing with meaning, I offer something entirely devoid of it: just pets. Just GIFs.

The author is unknown—neither famous nor celebrated, as is often the case in art.
The only meaning here is the one we choose to give to each creation.
What do you see in them? Everyone sees something unique.

And that is the essence of all art.

collections.name: Collection Rare 1
collections.description: The Collection consists of a single, 1 of 1 unique NFT. This digital asset serves as a replica of a physical oil painting on linen canvas, measuring 78 by 78 cm, and is elegantly framed in a wooden float frame that measures 80 by 80 by 4.3 cm. Titled “Prayer-Hope,” the painting encapsulates a moment of despair and confusion, where the human soul quietly whispers a prayer while the mind is filled with hope and light. The NFT image file is of high resolution, allowing to produce high-quality reproductions. We invite buyers to enter into a one-page agreement to license the production of reproductions and other commercial uses. Our goal is to tokenize the original painting and prioritize the buyer of the mint for the opportunity to acquire ownership of the tokenized artwork.

collections.name: The Neon Warden Chronicles
collections.description:
Dive into the luminous world of Neon Warden, a mysterious guardian navigating the vibrant, chaotic landscapes of the Neonverse. Each piece in this collection unveils a new chapter in their journey, blending high-tech cyberpunk aesthetics with celestial energy. From towering spires to enigmatic underground realms, explore a future where light and shadows collide, and destiny is forged in neon.

The Neon Warden is a being forged at the intersection of humanity and technology, an enigmatic figure whose origins are whispered in fragments across the glowing streets of the Neonverse. Once an ordinary soul lost in the chaos of a crumbling world, the Warden was chosen—or perhaps created—by the Astra Core, an ancient golden orb that embodies the raw, untamed energy of the universe. The Astra Core fused with their very essence, gifting them extraordinary abilities to manipulate light, energy, and the digital frameworks of the Metaverse.

collections.name: CryptoZombies Genesis
collections.description:
CryptoZombies Genesis is a retro-inspired NFT collection, originally created in 2021 and never released—until now.

This exclusive mini-collection features only 100 original CryptoZombies, each embodying a nostalgic piece of NFT history. Their distinctive accessories draw inspiration from iconic collections like CryptoPunks, fused with unique and innovative touches. The collection includes special designs, beta prototypes, and even a rare concept version of a CryptoZombie.

By holding a CryptoZombie, you secure a spot on our exclusive waitlist for future groundbreaking creative projects. This is more than an NFT—it’s your ticket to the next chapter of digital art evolution. Don’t miss your chance to be part of this historic launch!

collections.description:
Welcome to Pets in Olympics, a one-of-a-kind NFT collection celebrating the playful spirit of our furry friends as they take on the thrill of the Olympic Games! This collection captures delightful moments of cats, dogs and rabbits participating in a variety of Olympic events - from track and field to swimming, gymnastics, and beyond.

Each NFT is thoughtfully designed to showcase the charm, energy, and imagination of pets as they compete, bringing together the worlds of sports and animal lovers in a creative and heartwarming way. Whether you're a pet enthusiast, a sports fan, or an NFT collector, Pets in Olympics offers a playful and inspiring addition to your digital collection.

Join the movement to celebrate the joy and athleticism of our animal companions and own a piece of this unique and whimsical universe!

Get ready to cheer on your favourite furry Olympians. Let the games begin!

As a pet lover, 10% of profits generated from sales of 67 NFTs will be donated to HKSPCA.

collections.name: 7SeasOwls
collections.description: Inspired by ancient mythology and the hidden origins of the world's history, this unique collection explores the roots of humanity and its ultimate destinies. It begins with a spark of inspiration that arrives with the swiftness of light, at precisely the right moment. So fleeting is this inspiration that, if not transformed into an art form, it risks being lost to the mysteries of darkness. From this process, as life takes shape and an art form emerges—one that is devoid of memories of its own beginnings—it embarks on a journey akin to navigating the vast ocean of wisdom. In this endeavor, it strives for righteousness and understanding in the pursuit of a better world.

collections.name: Part Time Lives of Pepe
collections.description:
Part-Time Lives of Pepe is the inaugural NFT collection by Sideprojects, blending the iconic Pepe the Frog meme with a journey through time and digital culture. This collection celebrates Pepe's rich history, from its early internet roots to its evolution into a prominent symbol in the world of meme coins and Web3. With a unique blend of humor, nostalgia, and innovation, Part-Time Lives of Pepe reimagines the meme as a time-traveling character, each NFT showcasing a different era and personality of Pepe through artistic interpretations.

This collection isn't just about art – it's a tribute to the meme culture that shaped the modern digital landscape, with a special nod to the rise of the Pepe coin in the cryptocurrency world. By combining our passion for NFTs, Web3, and the ever-evolving meme culture, we aim to inspire others to embrace the playful side of the digital revolution and dive deeper into the limitless possibilities of crypto, community, and creativity.

collections.name: Zargaroff Art
collections.description: This collection showcases the resilient spirit and artistic talent of Nava Zargaroff. After a life-changing accident in her 60s that resulted in impaired mobility and chronic pain, she found solace and self-expression through art. This collection features a diverse range of pieces, showcasing her mastery of various mediums, including acrylics, oils, and more. From the intricate detail of pointillism to the bold strokes of abstract forms and other artistic styles, offering a rich and varied artistic experience. Each piece in this collection is a testament to her perseverance and the healing power of creativity.
